        <abstract> 
<p>Discusses proposed survey of Glen Roy. Mentions Glen Roy theories of Agassiz and William Buckland. Includes a memorandum calling for a careful survey of the parallel roads of Glen Roy. Mentions M. A. Bravais ["On the lines of ancient level of the sea in Finmark", <hi rend="italic">Q. J. Geol. Soc. Lond.</hi> 1 (1845): 534].</p> 
